<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.3">
<l>tūṅkār piṟavik kaḷiṉṉam pukappeytu,</l>
<l>vāṅkā yeṉṟucin tittunā  ṉataṟkañci</l>
<l>pāmpō ṭorukū raiyilē payiṉṟāṟpōl</l>
<l>tāṅkā tuḷḷamtaḷ ḷumeṉtā maraikkaṇṇā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Worrying that you will not rescue [me], dumping [me] again</l>
<l>Into difficult oscillating births, [and] fearing for that,</l>
<l>As if staying in a hut with snakes, my lotus-eye [lord],</l>
<l>Being unable to bear [it], my mind reels.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
